      "widgets_values": [
        "IMAGE TO STORYBOARD + VIDEO\n\nTo use this workflow, simply add your prompt for your scene and an optional reference image. Your prompt will be expanded to create a 9 part storyboard and a video from Sora.\n\nDue to Sora's moderation rules, you cannot use realistic humans as direct image input. So if you want to make a scene with realistic humans set the \"use storyboard image\" toggle to False. In this case you will also not receive a storyboard output, and will just receive a video. You will still use the reference image input in this case as it will still be used to generate a description.\n\nFor better video quality and possibly better prompt adherence you can set the model dropdown above to sora-2-pro\n\nFor this workflow to work make sure you have the SoraUtils nodes installed in your custom_nodes folder"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
